ingredients.name: Dirt
ingredients.description: Dry, wet, hard, soft. Dirt is dirt.

ingredients.name: Iron
ingredients.description: A common, heavy, hard metal. Found in mines and a favourite of warriors the world over.

ingredients.name: Gold
ingredients.description: A rare, heavy, precious metal. A dwarfs first love, and a friend of nobels.

ingredients.name: Silver
ingredients.description: A semi-rare, heavy, precious metal. A friend of tradesmen and the vain.

ingredients.name: Copper
ingredients.description: A common, light-weight metal. A friend of the working class and engineers.

ingredients.name: Mercury
ingredients.description: A rare, liquid metal. Said to be the tears of the gods and known to promote vitality.

ingredients.name: Coal
ingredients.description: A dense, combustible black rock. Valued highly by Dwarfs.

ingredients.name: Wood
ingredients.description: A lightweight product of trees and plants. 'A woodelfs first girlfriend' - Common saying in Nordland
